      <div xml:id="TheRoseFamily"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="Free"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="Happy"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="Nature"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
              <l>The rose is a rose,</l>
          <l>And was always a rose.</l> 
          <l>But the theory now goes,</l>
          <l>That the apple's now a rose.</l>
          <l>And the pear is, and so's.</l>
          <l>The plum, I suppose,</l>
          <l>The dear only knows.</l>
          <l>What will next prove a rose.</l>
          <l>You, of course, are a rose.</l>
          <l>But were always a rose.</l>
          
                 
